    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Nepinnotheres fulvia sp. nov., male holotype, cl 2.8 mm, cw 2.9 mm, ZRC 2018.1391. A, dorsal habitus; B, right maxilliped 3; C, anterior cephalothorax; D, anterior thoracic sternum and anterior pleon; E, right chela; F–I, right P2–5; J, right P2 proximal articles, ventral view; K, pleon; L, left G1, pleonal view; M, left G2, pleonal view. Scales: A = 1.0 mm; B, L, M = 0.25 mm; C–K = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954459/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954461>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Nepinnotheres fulvia sp. nov., female paratype, cl 3.0 mm, cw 3.1 mm, ZRC 2018.1392. A, dorsal habitus; B, right maxilliped 3; C, anterior cephalothorax; D, anterior thoracic sternum; E, right chela; F–I, right P2–5; J, right P2 proximal articles, ventral view; K, pleon. Scales: A, K = 1.0 mm; B = 0.25 mm; C–J = 0.5 mm." ;
